   "explain_zh": "指颜色“黑色”，可用于事物或抽象概念（如黑暗）。\n\n例：黒い猫がいます。\n有一只黑猫。",
   "explain_en": "Means 'black'. Describes dark objects or abstract concepts like darkness.\n\n例：黒い猫がいます。\nThere is a black cat.",
